---
title: Mexican Spiced Halloumi with Quinoa, Black Beans and Coriander
description: The Mexican seasoning on this halloumi is something of a taste sensation, taking this simple twenty minute dish to showstopper status. And Chef Andre’s talents don’t stop there - nutty quinoa, juicy tomatoes, a kick of fresh zesty lime and peppery rocket are the dream accompaniments to this deliciously nutritious weeknight dinner. We’ll pass your compliments to the Chef!
